    mc("'Triangulation' in research methodology means:","Drawing a triangle diagram","Using multiple data sources, methods, or researchers to cross-check findings and increase credibility","Interviewing three participants","A statistical technique",1,"Triangulation: using multiple sources of evidence to corroborate findings. Method triangulation (interview + observation + document analysis) strengthens credibility and reduces bias."),
